{
  "stem": "1975.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he served in the Lithuanian Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was also a factor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had many, many friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had prevented us to-- but we were not sure until the last minute.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So me being in waiting to get my diploma, and the fact also that in our house, where we lived in Kaunas, they have also assessed that each house, they felt that people should not occupy too much room.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to allocate an amount of square footage or square meters for each family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in our house, they have placed two Russian pilots who lived together with us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to give them, for free, a space.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to live together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were very nice and very friendly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But suddenly on June 20, the night of June, 20, 1941, there was an alarm.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the middle of the night, we heard the Russian pilots have-- were very disturbed, and they were being called, and they had to rush to the airport.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That same night, the airport from Kaunas, which was the capital of Lithuania, was bombed by the German aviation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And unfortunately, the Russians didn't have time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So now, I mean, this war started without any notification, without any advance or advice, or-- it was a-- a sudden decision by-- by the Nazi commanders, run by the Hitler regime, to-- to attack Russia.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were the first one being attacked, because Lithuania had a border with Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they have destroyed the few planes that Russia had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the fact also, Russia had some troops in Lithuania, especially in Kaunas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the troops were also not too well prepared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They looked very good for the small Lithuanian country.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
